data.description: This home is a year old in a great location and great condition, still has builder warranty. Area is growing with a new park around the corner, also within close proximity to stores and a police station. you can feel the love in this house as you walk through the doors, very well maintained. with four bedrooms and three bathrooms this home has a lot of space inside and out.
